@CloudAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5109
@access_token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Health (anonymous)
GET {{CloudAPI_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Who am I (requires Bearer token from cloud_idp)
GET {{CloudAPI_HostAddress}}/api/whoami
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

###
